#
# etc/ndjbdns/ip/
#
# A file in this directory, named after an IP or a subnet address tells
# dnscached daemon to accept DNS requests from the said IP/subnet address.
#
# For ex:
#
#   File name : Action
# ===========================================================================
#
#   127.0.0.1 : tells dnscached to accept DNS request coming from 127.0.0.1.
#
#   192.168.1 : tells dnscached to accept DNS request coming from any of the
#               256 machines -> 192.168.1.0 to 192.168.1.255.
#
#
#   All DNS requests coming from any other IP addresses are not served by
#   default.
#
